    <item>
      <title>什么是相对强弱指数（RSI）？ --知识铺</title>
      <link>https://index.zshipu.com/stocktactics/post/20240615/%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E5%BC%BA%E5%BC%B1%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B0RSI--%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E9%93%BA/</link>
